channel.title: Hosting for one person, First come first serve. No Catch, Just feel like hosting
channel.description:
I am willing to host a server, Doesn't matter if it's 317 508 to 718. I am willing to host 24/7 cause i have nothing to do and my server fails. :P So pm me or reply to this happy PKING !
Portforwarded, Ready to Host.
No LAG.
